{"title":"根——谨以此诗献给抗击非典的同胞们","authors":["张维耕"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——谨以此诗献给抗击非典的同胞们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长了五千年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已把大地抓牢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你生长精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也生长脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐血雨历风霜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次灾难袭来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像听到进军的号角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个民族进行一次空前的凝聚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血浓于水的感人故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次汹汹而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次悻悻而去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈挫愈勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愈挫愈奋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你输送给子孙的品格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难只能让精神更丰富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难只能使脊梁更挺直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自你无比的坚韧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自你无悔的支撑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因你在生命不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因你在事业长存"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14}